                            <comment id="16319345" author="githubbot" created="Tue, 9 Jan 2018 22:51:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;junrao closed pull request #4406: &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-4247&quot; title=&quot;kafka-run-class has potential to add a leading colon to classpath&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-4247&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-4247&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Prevent CLASSPATH from beginning with a single colon&lt;br/&gt;
